=== DIGITAL_SHRINE ===
# id: 72
# title: The Digital Shrine
# chinese_title: 数字神社
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

A holographic shrine flickers in a quiet corner of the station. Digital incense burns without smoke, and pixel-rendered offerings sit before a screen displaying the names of the departed. Someone has maintained this memorial through decades of abandonment.

* [Light a digital incense stick]
  ~ gain_radical("火")
  "香" (xiāng) — incense, fragrant. The radical "火" relates to burning.
* [Read the names of the honored dead]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "敬" (jìng) — respect, to honor
* [Search for who has been maintaining the shrine]
  ~ gain_item("credit_chip")
  "谁" (shéi) — who
